reviews.review_text: 10th row fun show jerry loses voice at the end of black peter slams mic down turns around to his amp an takes it out on guitar comes out of it smilin very cool to see up close
Laryngitis Garcia struggled with a tough case of laryngitis all night.  Bobby Brent and Phil all stepped up to make this a great show!!
